org.proteininformationresource.siterule.model
Interface SiteRuleManager

All Known Implementing Classes:
SiteRuleManagerImpl
public interface SiteRuleManager

Author: Chuming Chen
University of Delaware
Center for Bioinformatics and Computational Biology
Date: July 16, 2013

A SiteRuleManager manages a set of Site Rules. It is the main point for creating, loading and accessing Site Rules.
